# Functional Core (Hard Rule)

- No `class`, `this`, or OOP. Pure functions and closures only.
- Logic in `lib/` and `services/`; UI in `app/` and `components/` only renders and dispatches (no business decisions or side-effect orchestration in components).
- Immutable: `Readonly<>`, no in-place mutation. Updates via spread or `structuredClone`. State setters replace state: `set(s => ({ ...s, newKey: value }))`; never mutate nested refs.

```ts
// ✅
function mergeTranscript(prev: TranscriptEntry[], next: TranscriptEntry): TranscriptEntry[] {
  return [...prev, next];
}
set(prev => ({ ...prev, nodes: [...prev.nodes, node] }));
```
